{"tid":1307209,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌泳池倒掛五星旗　康文署稱會監察","createTime":"2019-07-11T12:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T13:01:43.000Z","uid":41404,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"990a66ad5211e5fd12d006f4671e92cbc4a5c427","tid":1307209,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190711/photo/bkn-20190711170255317-0711_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190711172333\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190711%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190711170255317-0711_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190711172333&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjq0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=73f229c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190711/photo/bkn-20190711170255317-0711_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190711172333</a><br />\n<br />\n今晨(11日)9時許，有市民途經東涌游泳池，發現泳池五星旗倒轉懸掛，五粒星被倒轉向下，旁邊的區旗則掛得正確。負責管理泳池的康樂及文化事務署承認倒掛五星旗，對此表示歉意，並會加強監察員工進行懸掛國旗的工作。<br />\n<br />\n康文署回覆東網查詢時表示，根據既定程序，康文署場地員工進行升五星旗工作時，須有一名場地管理人員在旁監督，以確保程序正確。今早東涌游泳池場地管理人員因需處理一宗投訴事件，致未能監察升旗過程，隨後巡查時發現錯誤，已即時作出糾正及掛回正確方向。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190711/bkn-20190711170255317-0711_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190711%2Fbkn-20190711170255317-0711_00822_001.html&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjq0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=599637d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190711/bkn-20190711170255317-0711_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2a905b3df8badbcfc87545d19efd4175c421a552","tid":1307209,"uid":41404,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190711/photo/bkn-20190711170255317-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190711172333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190711%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190711170255317-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190711172333&h=a30019a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東涌游泳池今日倒掛五星旗。"},{"pid":"736f10f92973b1757a050518b31ae8f63dc44ef3","tid":1307209,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c443a382c0d38f9161d9668326c467cd35105f48","tid":1307209,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},{"pid":"ef3e9379bb5788ad7fee0ed90b1384fccc25051e","tid":1307209,"uid":997,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:50:31.000Z","msg":"唔信係冇心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eba07a928d894b2134e0de8ceca701c65889fc1","tid":1307209,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff24268580a676465f4a56fb45c3bbda94e3356","tid":1307209,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:52:33.000Z","msg":"返工做錯野好平常姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81102cd7a319fe8e00bba0294c5199147299b98a","tid":1307209,"uid":69841,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190711/large/1562831300_e467.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190711%2Flarge%2F1562831300_e467.jpg&h=b836b914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟隨警方指引啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4bf4a971dbc95811d986ec254e54c6bd9ced30","tid":1307209,"uid":165683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ef3e9379bb5788ad7fee0ed90b1384fccc25051e","tid":1307209,"uid